Wɔwoo John Kofi Agyekum Kufuor Mumu-Ɔpɛnimba 8 afe 1938.

Nna ne maame yɛ [[Gaana]]ni. Ne papa so nna ɔyɛ Gaanani.

Ɔsuaa ade wɔ Osei Tutu Boarding School [1951-1953]; Prempeh College [1954-1958]; Lincoln’s Inn - London [1959-1961] na Exeter College - University of Oxford [1961-1964].
Dea J A Kufuor yɛɛ a ɛma ne din terɛw ne sɛ ɔdii nkonim wɔ Gaana abatow a ɛdi kan a tumi firii aban dadaw hɔ asomdwee mu. Abere no, na ɔyɛ Gaana ɔmanpanin [2001-2004; 2004-2008].

